# Interview Questions

## Java Streams & Collections

Given an Employee object with the following fields:

```java
Employee {
    Long id;
    String name;
    Double salary;
    String department;
}
```

### 1. Top 5 Highest Salaried Employees

* How will you find the top 5 highest salaried employees using Java Streams?
* How will you return the complete Employee objects instead of just salaries?

### 2. Highest Salary in Each Department

* How will you find the employee with the highest salary in each department?
* How will you return a Map<Department, Employee>?

### 3. First Non-Repeated Character

* Find the first non-repeated character in a String without using Streams.
* What would be the time and space complexity?

